{"chapter_number":75,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":31,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"القيامة","name_complex":"Al-Qiyāmah","name_simple":"Al-Qiyamah","verses_count":40,"pages":[577,578],"meaning":{"text":"The Resurrection","en":"The Resurrection","id":"Hari Berbangkit"},"verses":[[[1,5552,"75:1","لَا أُقْسِمُ بِيَوْمِ الْقِيَامَةِ",["Nay! I swear by the day of resurrection.","Aku bersumpah dengan hari Kiamat,"],577,29,58,231,null,null],[2,5553,"75:2","وَلَا أُقْسِمُ بِالنَّفْسِ اللَّوَّامَةِ",["Nay! I swear by the self-accusing soul.","dan aku bersumpah demi jiwa yang selalu menyesali (dirinya sendiri)."],577,29,58,231,null,null],[3,5554,"75:3","أَيَحْسَبُ الْإِنسَانُ أَلَّن نَّجْمَعَ عِظَامَهُ",["Does man think that We shall not gather his bones?","Apakah manusia mengira bahwa Kami tidak akan mengumpulkan (kembali) tulang-belulangnya?"],577,29,58,231,null,null],[4,5555,"75:4","بَلَىٰ قَادِرِينَ عَلَىٰ أَن نُّسَوِّيَ بَنَانَهُ",["Yea! We are able to make complete his very fingertips","(Bahkan) Kami mampu menyusun (kembali) jari-jemarinya dengan sempurna."],577,29,58,231,null,null],[5,5556,"75:5","بَلْ يُرِيدُ الْإِنسَانُ لِيَفْجُرَ أَمَامَهُ",["Nay! man desires to give the lie to what is before him.","Tetapi manusia hendak membuat maksiat terus-menerus."],577,29,58,231,null,null],[6,5557,"75:6","يَسْأَلُ أَيَّانَ يَوْمُ الْقِيَامَةِ",["He asks: When is the day of resurrection?","Dia bertanya, “Kapankah hari Kiamat itu?”"],577,29,58,231,null,null],[7,5558,"75:7","فَإِذَا بَرِقَ الْبَصَرُ",["So when the sight becomes dazed,","Maka apabila mata terbelalak (ketakutan),"],577,29,58,231,null,null],[8,5559,"75:8","وَخَسَفَ الْقَمَرُ",["And the moon becomes dark,","dan bulan pun telah hilang cahayanya,"],577,29,58,231,null,null],[9,5560,"75:9","وَجُمِعَ الشَّمْسُ وَالْقَمَرُ",["And the sun and the moon are brought together,","lalu matahari dan bulan dikumpulkan,"],577,29,58,231,null,null],[10,5561,"75:10","يَقُولُ الْإِنسَانُ يَوْمَئِذٍ أَيْنَ الْمَفَرُّ",["Man shall say on that day: Whither to fly to?","pada hari itu manusia berkata, “Ke mana tempat lari?”"],577,29,58,231,null,null],[11,5562,"75:11","كَلَّا لَا وَزَرَ",["By no means! there shall be no place of refuge!","Tidak! Tidak ada tempat berlindung!"],577,29,58,231,null,null],[12,5563,"75:12","إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوْمَئِذٍ الْمُسْتَقَرُّ",["With your Lord alone shall on that day be the place of rest.","Hanya kepada Tuhanmu tempat kembali pada hari itu."],577,29,58,231,null,null],[13,5564,"75:13","يُنَبَّأُ الْإِنسَانُ يَوْمَئِذٍ بِمَا قَدَّمَ وَأَخَّرَ",["Man shall on that day be informed of what he sent before and (what he) put off.","Pada hari itu diberitakan kepada manusia apa yang telah dikerjakannya dan apa yang dilalaikannya."],577,29,58,231,null,null],[14,5565,"75:14","بَلِ الْإِنسَانُ عَلَىٰ نَفْسِهِ بَصِيرَةٌ",["Nay! man is evidence against himself,","Bahkan manusia menjadi saksi atas dirinya sendiri,"],577,29,58,231,null,null],[15,5566,"75:15","وَلَوْ أَلْقَىٰ مَعَاذِيرَهُ",["Though he puts forth his excuses.","dan meskipun dia mengemukakan alasan-alasannya."],577,29,58,231,null,null],[16,5567,"75:16","لَا تُحَرِّكْ بِهِ لِسَانَكَ لِتَعْجَلَ بِهِ",["Do not move your tongue with it to make haste with it,","Jangan engkau (Muhammad) gerakkan lidahmu (untuk membaca Al-Qur'an) karena hendak cepat-cepat (menguasai)nya."],577,29,58,231,null,null],[17,5568,"75:17","إِنَّ عَلَيْنَا جَمْعَهُ وَقُرْآنَهُ",["Surely on Us (devolves) the collecting of it and the reciting of it.","Sesungguhnya Kami yang akan mengumpulkannya (di dadamu) dan membacakannya."],577,29,58,231,null,null],[18,5569,"75:18","فَإِذَا قَرَأْنَاهُ فَاتَّبِعْ قُرْآنَهُ",["Therefore when We have recited it, follow its recitation.","Apabila Kami telah selesai membacakannya maka ikutilah bacaannya itu."],577,29,58,231,null,null],[19,5570,"75:19","ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيْنَا بَيَانَهُ",["Again on Us (devolves) the explaining of it.","Kemudian sesungguhnya Kami yang akan menjelaskannya."],577,29,58,231,null,null],[20,5571,"75:20","كَلَّا بَلْ تُحِبُّونَ الْعَاجِلَةَ",["Nay! But you love the present life,","Tidak! Bahkan kamu mencintai kehidupan dunia,"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[21,5572,"75:21","وَتَذَرُونَ الْآخِرَةَ",["And neglect the hereafter.","dan mengabaikan (kehidupan) akhirat."],578,29,58,231,null,null],[22,5573,"75:22","وُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ نَّاضِرَةٌ",["(Some) faces on that day shall be bright,","Wajah-wajah (orang mukmin) pada hari itu berseri-seri,"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[23,5574,"75:23","إِلَىٰ رَبِّهَا نَاظِرَةٌ",["Looking to their Lord.","memandang Tuhannya."],578,29,58,231,null,null],[24,5575,"75:24","وَوُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ بَاسِرَةٌ",["And (other) faces on that day shall be gloomy,","Dan wajah-wajah (orang kafir) pada hari itu muram,"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[25,5576,"75:25","تَظُنُّ أَن يُفْعَلَ بِهَا فَاقِرَةٌ",["Knowing that there will be made to befall them some great calamity.","mereka yakin bahwa akan ditimpakan kepadanya malapetaka yang sangat dahsyat."],578,29,58,231,null,null],[26,5577,"75:26","كَلَّا إِذَا بَلَغَتِ التَّرَاقِيَ",["Nay! When it comes up to the throat,","Tidak! Apabila (nyawa) telah sampai ke kerongkongan,"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[27,5578,"75:27","وَقِيلَ مَنْ ۜ رَاقٍ",["And it is said: Who will be a magician?","dan dikatakan (kepadanya), “Siapa yang dapat menyembuhkan?”"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[28,5579,"75:28","وَظَنَّ أَنَّهُ الْفِرَاقُ",["And he is sure that it is the (hour of) parting","Dan dia yakin bahwa itulah waktu perpisahan (dengan dunia),"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[29,5580,"75:29","وَالْتَفَّتِ السَّاقُ بِالسَّاقِ",["And affliction is combined with affliction;","dan bertaut betis (kiri) dengan betis (kanan),"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[30,5581,"75:30","إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوْمَئِذٍ الْمَسَاقُ",["To your Lord on that day shall be the driving.","kepada Tuhanmulah pada hari itu kamu dihalau."],578,29,58,231,null,null],[31,5582,"75:31","فَلَا صَدَّقَ وَلَا صَلَّىٰ",["So he did not accept the truth, nor did he pray,","Karena dia (dahulu) tidak mau membenarkan (Al-Qur'an dan Rasul) dan tidak mau melaksanakan shalat,"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[32,5583,"75:32","وَلَٰكِن كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ",["But called the truth a lie and turned back,","tetapi justru dia mendustakan (Rasul) dan berpaling (dari kebenaran),"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[33,5584,"75:33","ثُمَّ ذَهَبَ إِلَىٰ أَهْلِهِ يَتَمَطَّىٰ",["Then he went to his followers, walking away in haughtiness.","kemudian dia pergi kepada keluarganya dengan sombong."],578,29,58,231,null,null],[34,5585,"75:34","أَوْلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوْلَىٰ",["Nearer to you (is destruction) and nearer,","Celakalah kamu! Maka celakalah!"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[35,5586,"75:35","ثُمَّ أَوْلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوْلَىٰ",["Again (consider how) nearer to you and nearer.","Sekali lagi, celakalah kamu (manusia)! Maka celakalah!"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[36,5587,"75:36","أَيَحْسَبُ الْإِنسَانُ أَن يُتْرَكَ سُدًى",["Does man think that he is to be left to wander without an aim?","Apakah manusia mengira, dia akan dibiarkan begitu saja (tanpa pertanggungjawaban)?"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[37,5588,"75:37","أَلَمْ يَكُ نُطْفَةً مِّن مَّنِيٍّ يُمْنَىٰ",["Was he not a small seed in the seminal elements,","Bukankah dia mulanya hanya setetes mani yang ditumpahkan (ke dalam rahim),"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[38,5589,"75:38","ثُمَّ كَانَ عَلَقَةً فَخَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ",["Then he was a clot of blood, so He created (him) then made (him) perfect.","kemudian (mani itu) menjadi sesuatu yang melekat, lalu Allah menciptakannya dan menyempurnakannya,"],578,29,58,231,null,null],[39,5590,"75:39","فَجَعَلَ مِنْهُ الزَّوْجَيْنِ الذَّكَرَ وَالْأُنثَىٰ",["Then He made of him two kinds, the male and the female.","lalu Dia menjadikan darinya sepasang laki-laki dan perempuan."],578,29,58,231,null,null],[40,5591,"75:40","أَلَيْسَ ذَٰلِكَ بِقَادِرٍ عَلَىٰ أَن يُحْيِيَ الْمَوْتَىٰ",["Is not He able to give life to the dead?","Bukankah (Allah yang berbuat) demikian berkuasa (pula) menghidupkan orang mati?"],578,29,58,231,null,null]],[[[1,8,577,"&#xfb8a;","word","لَا",["Nay",""]],[2,8,577,"&#xfb8b;","word","أُقْسِمُ",["I swear",""]],[3,8,577,"&#xfb8c;","word","بِيَوْمِ",["by (the) Day",""]],[4,8,577,"&#xfb8d;","word","الْقِيَامَةِ",["(of) the Resurrection",""]],[5,8,577,"&#xfb8e;","end","ﮎ",[null,null]]],[[1,8,577,"&#xfb8f;","word","وَلَا",["And nay","dan benar-benar"]],[2,8,577,"&#xfb90;","word","أُقْسِمُ",["I swear","aku bersumpah"]],[3,8,577,"&#xfb91;","word","بِالنَّفْسِ",["by the soul","dengan jiwa"]],[4,8,577,"&#xfb92;","word","اللَّوَّامَةِ",["self-accusing","mencela/menyesali"]],[5,8,577,"&#xfb93;","end","ﮓ",[null,null]]],[[1,8,577,"&#xfb94;","word","أَيَحْسَبُ",["Does think","apakah mengira"]],[2,9,577,"&#xfb95;","word","الْإِنْسَانُ",["[the] man","manusia"]],[3,9,577,"&#xfb96;","word","أَلَّنْ",["that not","bahwa tidak"]],[4,9,577,"&#xfb97;","word","نَجْمَعَ",["We will assemble","Kami mengumpulkan"]],[5,9,577,"&#xfb98;","word","عِظَامَهُ",["his bones","tulang-belulangnya"]],[6,9,577,"&#xfb99;","end","ﮙ",[null,null]]],[[1,9,577,"&#xfb9a;","word","بَلَىٰ",["Nay","yang benar/bahkan"]],[2,9,577,"&#xfb9b;","word","قَادِرِينَ",["(We are) Able","berkuasa"]],[3,9,577,"&#xfb9c;","word","عَلَىٰ",["on","atas"]],[4,9,577,"&#xfb9d;","word","أَنْ",["that","dari"]],[5,9,577,"&#xfb9e;","word","نُسَوِّيَ",["We can restore","Kami menyempurnakan"]],[6,9,577,"&#xfb9f;","word","بَنَانَهُ",["his fingertips","jari-jemarinya"]],[7,9,577,"&#xfba0;","end","ﮠ",[null,null]]],[[1,9,577,"&#xfba1;","word","بَلْ",["Nay","bahkan"]],[2,10,577,"&#xfba2;","word","يُرِيدُ",["Desires","menghendaki"]],[3,10,577,"&#xfba3;","word","الْإِنْسَانُ",["[the] man","manusia"]],[4,10,577,"&#xfba4;","word","لِيَفْجُرَ",["to give (the) lie","untuk membuat durhaka"]],[5,10,577,"&#xfba5;","word","أَمَامَهُ",["(to) what is before him","di hadapannya/di masa depan"]],[6,10,577,"&#xfba6;","end","ﮦ",[null,null]]],[[1,10,577,"&#xfba7;","word","يَسْأَلُ",["He asks","ia bertanya"]],[2,10,577,"&#xfba8;","word","أَ